1. Purpose

This repository and all materials contained in it are created for participation in the 2026 AI for Future Talent Competition, Anker Innovation Track.

The materials include, but are not limited to, source code, Agent Skills, prompts, schemas, scripts, workflows, research methods, product concepts, product specifications, reports, diagrams, datasets, templates, documentation, and experimental designs.

