The competition organizers, authorized judges, mentors, and representatives of Anker Innovations are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable permission to access, execute, reproduce internally, and evaluate the materials solely for the following purposes:

* competition registration and eligibility review;
* technical and product evaluation;
* judging, mentoring, presentation, and award administration;
* verification of the submitted project's functionality and originality.

This permission does not transfer ownership of any intellectual property.

